cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.ET, cs.SY, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the environmental impact and financial cost of deep learning research, and proposes solutions to make AI more efficient and inclusive. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also touches on topics related to energy efficiency (cs.ET), system engineering (cs.SY), and software engineering (cs.SE).
